id":1821201,"uid":69746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T07:35:35.000Z","msg":"2020年仲搵2018年嘅資料打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f7d22c9dba1f614b5f1cb250a7e539bc135899f","tid":1821201,"uid":162910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T07:36:59.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"afd782d06dab8ab40e7a140a240d9288c69d3371","tid":1821201,"uid":166032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T07:39:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb8095ad8697dc4673e739ab0434b74f16de4f1c","tid":1821201,"uid":8331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T07:55:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e3c4f2de750fd27c0a718ab0d42671a2e42874ac","tid":1821201,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T07:58:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2019個分黎自2017-2018年頭個情況</span><br />\n<br />\n佢係forward 亦有寫到對最近香港睇法, 相信之後個分會低<br />\n個分一直冇計算到<span style=\"color: red;\">Freedom of Domestic Movement</span><br />\nRule of Law 係2017年部分仲低過排第5嘅澳洲<br />\n<br />\n其他低分位關於政治:<br />\nLaws and Reg. That Influence Media 5.7分<br />\nPolitical Pressure, Control Media   5分<br />\n<br />\n安全嘅3大評分點<br />\n1. Homicide 兇殺 <br />\n2. Disappearance, Conflict, Terrorism 失踪，衝突，恐怖主義<br />\n3. Women's Security, Safety 婦女的安全，安全<br />\n<br />\n2017年香港相對和平先高, 之後應該會低返<br />\n第2項因為有Terrorism, 所以可能會拖得冇咁低<br />\n黑警唔好自欺欺人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vbfGPj6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvbfGPj6.png&h=5fc6392c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0ecd920fc2a6f3db070feca5ca564b52702c2e30","tid":1821201,"uid":73948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T07:59:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ea87cb